documentation.text:
addAdapter(adapter)
 Invariant:
 only owner expands execution surface

removeAdapter(adapter)
 Invariant:
 execution surface can only shrink, never mutate silently

deposit(amount)
 Invariant:
 shares minted are a pure function of current NAV

requestWithdraw(shares)
 Invariant:
 withdrawal intent is immutable per epoch

finalizeWithdraw(user)
 Invariant:
 withdrawals only settle after epoch finalization

adapterCall(adapter, data)
 Invariant:
 vault only executes whitelisted adapter code

typeDescriptions.typeString: function (uint256) view external returns (struct IReceiptRegistry.Receipt memory)

documentation.text:
dispute(epoch, proof)
 Invariant:
 provable inconsistency freezes the receipt

startEpoch()
 Invariant:
 snapshot reflects vault state at epoch start

finalizeEpoch()
 Invariant:
 snapshot reflects vault state at epoch end and becomes immutable

distribute(profit)
 Invariant:
 no inflation without realized profit
 cuts are immutable

typeDescriptions.typeString: function (struct ReceiptRegistry.Receipt calldata,bytes calldata) view returns (bool)

documentation.text:
submitReceipt(epoch, receipt, signature)
 Invariant:
 one receipt per epoch, signature-bound

freeze(epoch)
 Invariant:
 frozen receipts cannot be superseded
